<body>
    

    <div class="jumbotron text-center">
        <h1>ABOUT US</h1><br />
        <p>
            Welcome to Exposure's global platform. Our core philosophy is connecting workers with their potential employers.

            Our Mission is to help all Casual workers connect for commerce and collaboration.

            Exposure is a free platform which offers registered members a rich communication experience,
            integrated with jobs, eCommerce and community promotions.

            Start with messaging and grow to experience the rich features including the ability to create individual profiles to showcase who you are and what you have to offer.

            Exposures technology will ensure that only fresh, active and current data is delivered daily. We welcome your ongoing feedback which will enable us to always deliver the best application for you.

            We thank you for your support and trust that you will enjoy using our app.
        </p>

