                <h4><strong>MISSION:</strong> Our mission is to connect casual workers with their potential employers to break the cycle of unemployment. </h4>
                <p><strong>VISION:</strong> Our vision is to see Exposure being used in every city in South Africa and in time expand beyond the boundaries of the country.</p>
            </div>
